    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "idk, it just feels like you're romanticizing struggle. \"defiant heart\" doesn't change the fact that everything is doomed. it honestly feels more like a mercy to just step out early. if the whole world is just going to suffer and end, why is it better to stay and watch it happen? feels like everyone's just forcing themselves to stay through something that doesn't even have a hopeful ending.",
